%2c%e9%87%8d%e5%ae%b6%e8%b2%a1%e8%a8%b4%2c3%2c20211220%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDV,107,重家財訴,3,20211220,1","JYEAR":"107","JCASE":"重家財訴","JNO":"3","JDATE":"20211220","JTITLE":"夫妻剩餘財產分配"}